---
import DocLayout from '../../../layouts/DocLayout.astro';
import { agentmakoMeta } from '../../../lib/agentmakoMeta';
---
<DocLayout
  title={`agentmako tool catalog — ${agentmakoMeta.toolCountLabel} by category · agentmako`}
  description={`The full agentmako MCP tool catalog. ${agentmakoMeta.toolCountSentence} across context, code intelligence, Reef Engine, database, trace and flow, diagnostics, workflow, artifacts, and telemetry. Read or mutation, with input shapes.`}
  canonicalPath="/docs/tools/"
  ogImage="/assets/og.png"
  ogType="website"
  breadcrumbs={[{"name": "Home", "href": "/"}, {"name": "Docs", "href": "/docs/"}, {"name": "Tools", "href": "/docs/tools/"}]}
>
<header class="doc-page-header">
  <span class="eyebrow">Reference &middot; Tools</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:1rem;">The full <em>tool catalog</em>.</h1>
    <p class="doc-hero__sub">
      <strong>agentmako</strong> ships {agentmakoMeta.toolCountSentence}. Each tool is
      either <em>read-only</em> (queries the index, store, or live
      filesystem/DB) or a <em>mutation</em> (writes Mako state — index
      refresh, diagnostic persistence, ack ledger). Authoritative
      runtime catalog: <code>agentmako tool list</code>.
    </p>
</header>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="agents" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <a class="agent-card" href="./context.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Context</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Read</span><span>11 tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          mako_help, context_packet, tool_batch, reef_diff_impact,
          reef_scout, reef_inspect, and evidence confidence tools.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./code-intel.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Code intelligence</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Read/Write</span><span>10 tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          repo_map, cross_search, ast_find_pattern, live_text_search,
          symbols_of, imports_impact, and friends.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./reef.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Reef Engine</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Read/Write</span><span>21 tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          file_preflight, project_findings, project_open_loops,
          verification_state, rule packs, project conventions, and ack tools.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./database.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Database</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Read/Write</span><span>7 tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          db_table_schema, db_rls, db_rpc, schema_usage, tenant_leak_audit
          for Postgres / Supabase awareness.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./flow.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Trace &amp; flow</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Read</span><span>15+ tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          route_trace, trace_file, trace_table, trace_rpc, flow_map,
          graph_path, change_plan, auth_path, route_context, trace_error,
          neighborhoods, and composer traces.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a class="agent-card" href="./diagnostics.html">
        <div class="agent-card__head">
          <h3 class="agent-card__name">Diagnostics</h3>
          <span class="agent-card__arrow">↗</span>
        </div>
        <div class="agent-card__meta"><span>Mostly write</span><span>8 tools</span></div>
        <p class="agent-card__desc">
          lint_files, typescript_diagnostics, eslint_diagnostics,
          oxlint_diagnostics, biome_diagnostics, git_precommit_check.
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="callout" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      <strong>Source of truth</strong>
      The category pages here cover the most-used tools per category.
      For the complete current registry, run <code>agentmako tool list</code>
      after install — that's the authoritative runtime catalog and
      always matches your installed version. The full registry list
      also lives at
      <a href="https://github.com/drhalto/agentmako/blob/main/TOOLS.md" rel="noopener">TOOLS.md</a>
      in the public repo.
    </div>

    <div class="callout" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <strong>Tool result metadata</strong>
      Mako tools now return contextual <code>_hints</code> and MCP
      annotations such as read-only, idempotent, advisory, and
      preview-first write behavior. Agents should read those hints before
      choosing the next call.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</DocLayout>
